---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Mango Media"
  description="Read the Mango Media privacy policy to understand how we collect, use, and protect information submitted through our website."
  ogImage="/images/branding/mango-og.webp"
>
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden pt-16 pb-20 sm:pt-20 sm:pb-24 lg:pt-24 lg:pb-28">
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 -z-10">
      <div class="absolute left-[-8%] top-12 h-56 w-56 rounded-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle,rgba(254,205,76,0.34),transparent_65%)] blur-2xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute right-[-6%] top-0 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle,rgba(218,60,120,0.22),transparent_60%)] blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 h-64 w-64 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle,rgba(1,155,144,0.14),transparent_62%)] blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container-shell">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-black/8 bg-white/80 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-[rgb(var(--color-text-secondary))] shadow-soft backdrop-blur dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-white/5">
          <span class="inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full mango-gradient"></span>
          Legal
        </div>

        <h1 class="mt-6 font-nunito text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[rgb(var(--color-text))] sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
          Privacy Policy
        </h1>

        <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-base leading-8 text-[rgb(var(--color-text-secondary))] sm:text-lg">
          This Privacy Policy explains how Mango Media may collect, use, and protect information submitted through this website.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pb-20 sm:pb-24 lg:pb-28">
    <div class="container-shell">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl surface-panel radius-brand p-6 sm:p-8 lg:p-10">
        <div class="space-y-8 text-[rgb(var(--color-text-secondary))]">
          <section>
            <h2 class="font-nunito text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[rgb(var(--color-text))]">
              Information We Collect
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-8 sm:text-lg">
              Mango Media may collect information you voluntarily submit through contact forms, including your name, business name, email address, phone number, website or social media links, and any details you include in your message.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-nunito text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[rgb(var(--color-text))]">
              How We Use Information
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-8 sm:text-lg">
              We may use submitted information to respond to inquiries, communicate about services, evaluate project fit, improve our website experience, and provide follow-up related to Mango Media services.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-nunito text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[rgb(var(--color-text))]">
              Sharing of Information
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-8 sm:text-lg">
              Mango Media does not sell your personal information. Information may be shared only when necessary to operate the website, deliver services, process inquiries, or comply with legal obligations.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-nunito text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[rgb(var(--color-text))]">
              Cookies and Analytics
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-8 sm:text-lg">
              This website may use basic analytics, cookies, or similar technologies to understand traffic and improve performance. These tools may collect non-personal usage information such as browser type, device type, and pages visited.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-nunito text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[rgb(var(--color-text))]">
              Data Security
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-8 sm:text-lg">
              Mango Media takes reasonable steps to protect submitted information, but no internet-based transmission or storage system can be guaranteed to be completely secure.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-nunito text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[rgb(var(--color-text))]">
              Third-Party Services
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-8 sm:text-lg">
              This website may rely on third-party services for hosting, analytics, or form handling. Those providers may process information according to their own privacy policies.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-nunito text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[rgb(var(--color-text))]">
              Your Choices
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-8 sm:text-lg">
              If you would like to request updates or removal of information you have submitted through this website, you can contact Mango Media directly at
              <a
                href="mailto:contact@mangomedia305.com"
                class="font-semibold text-[rgb(var(--color-text))] transition-colors duration-200 hover:text-[rgb(var(--color-mango-pink))]"
              >
                contact@mangomedia305.com
              </a>.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-nunito text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[rgb(var(--color-text))]">
              Updates to This Policy
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-8 sm:text-lg">
              Mango Media may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be reflected on this page.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-nunito text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[rgb(var(--color-text))]">
              Contact
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-8 sm:text-lg">
              For privacy-related questions, contact:
            </p>
            <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-8 sm:text-lg">
              Mango Media<br />
              Miami, Florida<br />
              <a
                href="mailto:contact@mangomedia305.com"
                class="font-semibold text-[rgb(var(--color-text))] transition-colors duration-200 hover:text-[rgb(var(--color-mango-pink))]"
              >
                contact@mangomedia305.com
              </a>
            </p>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>